# Escalation Notifier - REST Client Test Cases
# 
# This file is a testing template for the [Arcova Engage] Engagement - Escalation 
# Notifier Power Automate flow. To use:
#   1. Replace <YOUR_FLOW_URL_HERE> with the HTTP POST URL from the flow's trigger card
#   2. Replace <TEST_ENGAGEMENT_GUID_HERE> with a valid Engagement GUID from Dataverse
#   3. Click "Send Request" above each POST block to execute
#
# Requires VS Code REST Client extension (Huachao Mao).
#
# WARNING: The flow URL contains an authentication signature - treat as a secret.
#          Do not commit a version of this file with the real URL populated.

### Escalation Notifier Test - Happy Path

POST <YOUR_FLOW_URL_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engagementId": "<TEST_ENGAGEMENT_GUID_HERE>",
  "escalationReason": "Client has requested immediate senior agent involvement due to a compliance audit deadline pulled forward by three weeks. The current agent's bandwidth cannot accommodate the compressed timeline."
}


### Escalation Notifier Test - Missing engagementId (defensive validation)

POST <YOUR_FLOW_URL_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "escalationReason": "This request is missing engagementId and should return 400"
}